---

# 🚀 Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Flood-Prediction.git
```

Move into the project directory

```bash
cd Flood-Prediction
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run the project

```bash
python flood_prediction.py
```

Run Flask

```bash
python app.py
```

Open

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

